ta-toc-id%3D%5C%223929da50-79b7-463a-8077-76a1cb20f7a3%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20nice%20to%20celebrate%20for%20a%20whole%20weekend%2C%20not%20just%20one%20night%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223199%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abby%20Price%20and%20husband%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20greenery%20arch%20on%20wedding%20day%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68adc745cfc04e97619c0648%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222133%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20wedding%20celebration%20didn't%20feel%20crammed%20into%20a%20few%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20it%20unfolded%20slowly.%3Cp%3ECarrie%20Coleman%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20Friday%20wedding%20in%20Charlottesville%2C%20many%20of%20our%20friends%20and%20family%20arrived%20early%20and%20booked%20longer%20hotel%20stays%20instead%20of%20flying%20in%20for%20a%20single%20night.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20treated%20the%20event%20like%20a%20mini%20vacation%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that%20mindset%20shift%20made%20a%20difference.%20%3Cspan%3EInstead%20of%20rushing%20through%20goodbyes%20or%20packing%20bags%20the%20morning%20after%20the%20reception%2C%20guests%20can%20wake%20up%20with%20nowhere%20to%20be%20in%20(for%20some)%20a%20new%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20unexpected%20joys%20of%20a%20Friday%20wedding%20is%20what%20comes%20after.%20That%20Saturday%20becomes%20a%20built-in%20buffer%20%E2%80%94%20no%20stress%2C%20no%20formal%20plans%2C%20just%20time%20to%20relax%20and%20enjoy%20being%20with%20the%20people%20who%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20day%20after%20our%20wedding%20was%20filled%20with%20casual%20conversations%2C%20shared%20meals%2C%20and%20lively%20moments%20we%20would%20have%20missed%20in%20a%20typical%20one-day%20timeline.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20many%20guests%20stayed%20in%20town%20longer%2C%20we%20had%20more%20chances%20to%20connect%20with%20them%20at%20coffee%20shops%2C%20on%20morning%20walks%2C%20and%20over%20impromptu%20dinners.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%20of%20cramming%20our%20wedding%20celebration%20into%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eit%20was%20extended%20in%20a%20way%20that%20felt%20natural%20and%20unrushed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%2C%20we%20received%20positive%20feedback%20from%20several%20friends%20who%20had%20an%20incredible%20weekend%20casually%20exploring%20a%20new%20destination%20on%20top%20of%20attending%20our%20wedding.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c5b09db-77c8-4c10-82c2-33e1b60bcf74%5C%22%3EFriday%20weddings%20aren't%20for%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20suggest%20you%20embrace%20them%20if%20you%20can%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223199%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Abby%20Price%20and%20husband%20laughing%20in%20front%20of%20vintage%20peach-colored%20Volkswagen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68adc761cfc04e97619c064a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222133%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20one-time%20decision%20quickly%20became%20something%20our%20family%20swears%20by.%3Cp%3ECarrie%20Coleman%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20wedding%20went%20so%20well%20that%20my%20husband's%20brother%20planned%20a%20Friday%20wedding%20a%20few%20years%20later%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20unofficially%20become%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-holiday-traditions-month-december-chaotic-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efamily%20tradition%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20think%20more%20couples%20(and%20guests)%20should%20consider%20the%20underrated%20beauty%20of%20them%2C%20especially%20if%20there's%20travel%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20now%20celebrated%20three%20Friday%20weddings%20in%20three%20different%20destinations%3A%20Charleston%2C%20Charlottesville%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22htt