he%20U.S.%20are%20preparing%20to%20file%20antitrust%20lawsuits%20alleging%20Google%20has%20abused%20its%20dominance%20of%20online%20search%20and%20advertising%20to%20stifle%20competition%20and%20and%20boost%20its%20profits%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20published%20Friday%2C%20May%2015%2C%202020.%20(AP%20Photo%2FMarcio%20Jose%20Sanchez%2C%20File)%3Cp%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle%20is%20%E2%80%A6%20feeling%20lucky%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20judge's%20ruling%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-antitrust-monopoly-doj-ruling-decision-chrome-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20penalties%20for%20its%20online%20search%20monopoly%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20leave%20the%20tech%20giant%20unscathed.%20Still%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-antitrust-monopoly-case-decision-winners-losers-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elargely%20avoided%20the%20severe%20punishments%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20prosecutor%2C%20the%20US%20government%2C%20was%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20how%20was%20Google%20punished%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-Google%20can't%20negotiate%20exclusive%20partnerships%20to%20be%20the%20default%20search%20engine.%20As%20a%20reminder%2C%20Google%20paid%20Apple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-apple-iphone-search-engine-safari-deal-20-billion-2022-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2420%20billion%20in%202022%20alone%20to%20be%20Safari's%20default%20engine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-Google%20needs%20to%20share%20its%20search%20index%20and%20user-interaction%20data%20with%20competitors.%20Rivals%20will%20now%20have%20the%20benefit%20of%20training%20up%20their%20own%20models%20with%20some%20of%20the%20troves%20of%20data%20Google%20has%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E-Google%20has%20to%20provide%20syndication%20services%20to%20