p%3EWe%20could%20see%20the%20same%20thing%20this%20time%20around%20with%20AI%2C%20says%20Henry%20Blodget.%20And%20he%20says%20that%20wouldn't%20be%20a%20bad%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlodget%20has%20a%20very%20particular%20perspective%20on%20booms%20and%20busts%2C%20since%20he%20was%20a%20central%20figure%20in%20the%20rise%20and%20fall%20of%20the%20first%20internet%20bubble.%20On%20the%20way%20up%2C%20he%20was%20a%20celebrated%20Wall%20Street%20analyst%3B%20afterward%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20charged%20him%20with%20fraud%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress%2F2003-56.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20complaint%20he%20settled%20without%20admitting%20or%20denying%20guilt%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20dot-com%20era%2C%20Blodget%20went%20on%20to%20found%20the%20publication%20you're%20reading%20now%20(I%20was%20his%20first%20hire)%2C%20and%20is%20now%20putting%20out%20his%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2F%40regenerator1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublication%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fsolutions-with-henry-blodget%2Fid1832076220%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epodcast%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlodget's%20bubble%20argument%20goes%20like%20this%3A%20We%20see%20them%20all%20the%20time%2C%20and%20they%20can%20often%20be%20a%20good%20thing%2C%20by%20focusing%20money%20and%20attention%20on%20important%20things.%20But%20they%20will%20also%20inevitably%20deflate%20%E2%80%94%20so%20the%20trick%20is%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20play%20them.%20Which%2C%20for%20most%20people%2C%20involves%20not%20playing%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlodget%20and%20I%20talked%20about%20the%20AI%20boom%20and%20his%20new%20media%20aspirations%20in%20the%20latest%20episode%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fwhy-henry-blodget-is-building-another-media-company%2Fid1080467174%3Fi%3D1000723698735%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChannels%3C%2Fa%3E%20podcast.%20What%20follows%20is%20an%20edited%20excerpt%20of%20our%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeter%20Kafka%3A%20You%20got%20a%20very%20close%20look%20at%20the%20internet%20bubble%20of%20the%201990s.%20How%20does%20it%20compare%20to%20what%20we're%20seeing%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Blodget%3A%20This%20bubble%20phenomenon%20is%20the%20way%20markets%20and%20technology%20innovate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20often%20portrayed%20as%20a%20morality%20play%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20gonna%20end!%20It's%20so%20stupid.%20All%20this%20money%20is%20gonna%20be%20burned%2C%20and%20people%20are%20losing%20their%20minds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20really%20going%20on%20is%20it's%20a%20huge%20R%26amp%3BD%20lab.%20Hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%2C%20probably%20trillions%20at%20this%20point%2C%20are%20being%20thrown%20at%20something%20that%20most%20of%20us%20recognize%20as%20a%20huge%20future%20opportunity%2C%20the%20same%20way%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20recognized%20the%20internet%20as%20a%20huge%20future%20opportunity%20in%20the%20mid-1990s%20to%20late%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20any%20R%26amp%3BD%2C%20most%20of%20the%20experiments%20are%20going%20to%20fail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20going%20to%20happen%20is%20that%20at%20some%20point%2C%20this%20amazing%20fundamental%20growth%20wave%20%E2%80%94%20which%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20amazing%2C%20people%20are%20buying%20and%20using%20these%20products%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20revenue%20being%20generated%20and%20so%20forth%20%E2%80%94%20at%20some%20point%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20get%20out%20ahead%20of%20ourselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20setback%2C%20and%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20reordering%20of%20everything%2C%20and%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20companies%20are%20going%20to%20fail.%20And%20then%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20companies%20or%20the%20survivors%20from%20this%20first%20crash%20will%20go%20on%20and%20inherit%20the%20earth%2C%20and%20AI%20will%20be%20%3Cem%3Ebigger%3C%2Fem%3E%20than%20everybody%20thinks%20it%20will%20be%2C%20although%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20the%20consensus.%20I%20think%20it's%20probably%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20only%20question%20is%20where%20are%20we%3F%20Are%20we%20in%201996%20or%201997%3F%20Or%20are%20we%20in%20the%20fall%20of%201999%2C%20right%20on%20the%20precipice%20of%20the%20crash%3F%20And%20what%20I%20will%20respectfully%20submit%20is%20that%20there%20is%20no%20way%20to%20be%20super-confident%20about%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20premise%20here%20is%20that%20AI%20is%20real%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20going%20away.%20But%20some%20bubbles%20are%20just%20bubbles%2C%20right%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investopedia.com%2Fterms%2Fd%2Fdutch_tulip_bulb_market_bubble.asp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%20bought%20tulips%20and%20they%20went%20up%20in%20value%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20Or%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Frecode%2F22907072%2Fweb3-crypto-nft-bitcoin-metaverse%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Every%20serious%20people%20thought%20Web3%20was%20a%20big%20deal%20worth%20taking%20seriously%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20It%20appears%20to%20have%20gone%20nowhere.%20Are%20you%20confident%20that%20AI%20is%20real%20and%20important%20things%20will%20come%20of%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20so.%20I%20look%20at%20the%20adoption%20of%20Chat%20GPT%20and%20Claude%20and%20some%20of%20the%20other%20models.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20fundamental%20adoption%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20people%20have%20pointed%20out%2C%20there%20is%20not%20enough%20adoption%20or%20revenue%20to%20even%20begin%20to%20fund%20the%20extraordinary%20capital%20expenditures%20that%20are%20being%20made%20to%20provide%20these%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20is%20worrisome%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fculture%2Fopen-questions%2Fwhat-if-ai-doesnt-get-much-better-than-this%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20models%20seem%20to%20be%20progressing%20more%20slowly%20than%20people%20thought%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20their%20usefulness%20is%20not%20increasing%20as%20fast%20as%20people%20thought.%20And%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2025%2F08%2F21%2Fai-wall-street-big-tech%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20companies%20are%20actually%20really%20struggling%20with%20how%20to%20use%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELike%20companies%20that%20started%20a%20website%20in%201999%20and%20then%20realized%20it%20didn't%20transform%20their%20business.%20They%20just%20had%20a%20website.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight.%20But%20it%20%3Cem%3Efeels%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20this%20is%20real.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20what%20Open%20AI%20is%20already%20doing%2C%20the%20fundamental%20product%20is%20going%20gangbusters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20the%20valuations%20of%20all%20these%20stocks%20is%20that%20they%20are%20priced%20for%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20growth%20continuing%20for%20decades.%20So%20if%20you%20run%20into%20a%20problem%20like%20AOL%20ran%20into%2C%20which%20was%20they%20couldn't%20make%20the%20transition%20from%20dial-up%20to%20broadband%2C%20their%20valuation%20is%20going%20to%20get%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnlike%20the%20web%20bubble%2C%20you%20can't%20really%20be%20a%20stock-picker%20this%20time%20around%3A%20If%20you%20want%20to%20invest%20in%20an%20AI%20company%2C%20you%20can%20buy%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20that's%20about%20it.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20you're%20a%20normal%20person%20and%20you're%20interested%20in%20AI%20and%20you%20think%20this%20is%20real%2C%20but%20also%20a%20bubble%2C%20what%20do%20you%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20us%2C%20the%20truth%20is%20you%20have%20a%20balanced%20portfolio%20of%20index%20funds%20with%20a%20good%2C%20healthy%20slug%20of%20cash%20and%20bonds%20in%20there.%20You%20don't%20bet%20on%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20makes%20this%20look%20very%20much%20like%20the%201990s%20bubble%20is%20how%20AI%20investing%20is%20now%20juicing%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20economy.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F08%2F27%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fai-investment-economic-growth.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20lot%20of%20the%20economic%20growth%20we're%20seeing%20right%20now%20is%20coming%20from%20these%20investments%20in%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Microsoft%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20a%20few%20others%20are%20investing%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20in%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpaulkedrosky.com%2Fhoney-ai-capex-ate-the-economy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPaul%20Kedrosky%20wrote%20a%20great%20piece%20about%20how%20everyone's%20saying%20it's%20just%20like%20the%20railroads%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20you%20make%20the%20big%20investment%20up%20front%20and%20then%20you%20get%20the%20benefits%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpaulkedrosky.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPaul%3C%2Fa%3E%20points%20out%2C%20this%20is%20not%20like%20laying%20a%20fiber%20line%20that%20is%20going%20to%20be%20great%20for%20the%20next%2025%20years%2C%20or%20a%20set%20of%20railroad%20tracks%20you%20can%20use%20over%20the%20next%20hundred%20years.%20These%20things%20have%20a%20three-to-four-year%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20Nvidia%20will%20come%20out%20with%20new%20chips.%20The%20current%20chips%20will%20be%20outmoded.%20A%20lot%20of%20this%20massive%20investment%20in%20data%20centers%20is%20going%20to%20be%20obsolete%20soon.%20There%20isn't%20a%20huge%20payback%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we%20are%20really%20setting%20up%20for%20a%20situation%20in%20which%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20fundamental%20performance%20is%20being%20juiced%20by%20every%20company%20in%20the%20world%20panicking%20and%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20gotta%20invest%20in%20AI%26quot%3B.%20And%20all%20venture%20capital%20money%20is%20going%20there%20and%20so%20forth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%2C%20that%20party%20is%20likely%20to%20stop%2C%20and%20when%20it%20does%2C%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20this%20big%20reordering.%20Lots%20of%20companies%20will%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20going%20to%20shock%20me%20if%20in%20seven%20years%20%5Bwe%20realize%5D%20OpenAI%20took%20a%20wrong%20turn%20two%20years%20ago%20and%20went%20down%20some%20path%2C%20and%20somebody%20else%20comes%20up%20with%20something%20new%20that%20is%20the%20Google%20of%20the%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Google%20didn't%20really%20appear%20until%202000.%20They%20missed%20the%20whole%201990s%2C%20and%20yet%20they%20were%20the%20one%20that%20you%20wanted%2C%20because%20they%20got%20it%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhenry-blodget-ai-bubble-boom-dotcom-interview-peter-kafka-2025-09%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756904573000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b833fbcfc04e97619c7489%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhenry-blodget-ai-bubble-boom-dotcom-interview-peter-kafka-2025-09%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We're%20in%20an%20AI%20boom.%20Is%20it%20going%20to%20play%20out%20like%20the%20first%20Internet%20boom%3F%20Probably%2C%20says%20Henry%20Blodget%2C%20who%20had%20a%20front-row%20seat%20in%20the%201990s.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhenry-blodget-ai-bubble-boom-dotcom-interview-peter-kafka-2025-09%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22