receded%20share%20jumps.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20average%203-month%20gain%20after%20such%20a%20signal%20is%2028%25%2C%20versus%2019%25%20normally.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20volatile%20year%20for%20shares%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-takeaways-from-the-nvidia-second-quarter-earnings-call-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20stock%20plunging%2031%25%20to%20start%20the%20year%20before%20rallying%2084%25%20since%20April%20lows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Pierson%2C%20the%20director%20of%20research%20at%20S3%20Partners%2C%20has%20found%20a%20fairly%20reliable%20way%20to%20capitalize%20on%20that%20volatility.%20Or%20rather%2C%20a%20metric%20to%20watch%20within%20the%20stock%20that%20serves%20as%20a%20signal%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-full-year-outlook-nvda-ai-chips-goldman-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoutsized%20gains%20ahead%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20called%20the%20long-to-short%20ratio%2C%20and%20it's%20calculated%20by%20taking%20a%20stock's%20active%20long%20interest%20and%20dividing%20it%20by%20short%20interest.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.s3partners.com%2Farticles%2Fnvda-positioning-signals-that-pay%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20Tuesday%2C%20Pierson%20found%20that%20following%20notable%20increases%20in%20the%20ratio%2C%20Nvidia's%20share%20price%20has%20typically%20surged%20over%20the%20following%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20specifically%2C%20when%20the%20ratio%20climbs%20to%201.5%20standard%20deviations%20above%20its%20six-month%20moving%20average%2C%20it's%20gone%20up%2011%25%20over%20the%20following%20month.%20That's%20nearly%20double%20the%20usual%20average%20monthly%20gain%20of%206%25.%20For%20the%20subsequent%20three-month%20period%2C%20following%20the%20signal%2C%20Nvidia%20has%20returned%2028%25%2C%20versus%2019%25%20normally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20saw%20gains%2086%25%20of%20the%20time%20in%20the%20month%20following%20a%20reading%20above%20the%201.5-standard-deviation%20threshold.%20When%20the%20stock%20saw%20rare%20losses%20during%20those%20periods%2C%20it%20only%20fell%20by%20an%20average%20of%201%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FDjD0a%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FDjD0a%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20findings%20led%20Pierson%20to%20call%20the%20ratio%20a%20%26quot%3Bpowerful%20short-to-intermediate-term%20tool%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20seems%20to%20lose%20its%20ability%20to%20predict%20returns%20beyond%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20chart%20showing%20the%20returns.%20Periods%20when%20the%20long-to-short%20ratio%20is%20at%20least%20at%201.5%20are%20shaded%20orange.%20Nvidia's%20stock%20returns%20are%20shown%20in%20the%20black%20line.%20Right%20now%2C%20the%20measure%20is%20below%20the%201.5%20standard-deviation%20threshold%20as%20the%20ratio%20of%20long%20positions%20to%20short%20positions%20has%20fallen%20in%20recent%20weeks%20to%2015.4.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221958%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22nvda%20long%20to%20short%20ratio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b73c7b194a2d49b8af92a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ES3%20Partners%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20has%20continued%20to%20be%20effective%20so%20far%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202025%20year-to-date%2C%20the%20LTS%20extreme%20signal%20has%20remained%20effective%3A%20across%2046%20threshold%20days%2C%20NVDA%20delivered%20an%20average%20%2B7%25%20forward%201M%20return%20with%20a%2076%25%20win%20rate%2C%20compared%20with%20just%20%2B5%25%20on%20all%20days%2C%20with%20a%2054%25%20win%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20Pierson%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%202025%2C%20periods%20of%20Long-to-Short%20crowding%20in%20NVIDIA%20have%20coincided%20with%20roughly%20double%20the%20baseline%201-month%20forward%20return.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20stock%20has%20had%20a%20rough%2010%20days%20after%20it%20warned%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-nvda-stock-earnings-call-report-live-updates-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eslowing%20growth%20ahead%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20its%20quarterly%20earnings%20call%20last%20week.%20Since%20August%2026%2C%20the%20stock%20is%20down%206.5%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20remains%20a%20favorite%20among%20investors.%20Brokerage%20platform%20Interactive%20Brokers%20said%20Nvidia%20was%20the%20most%20bought%20stock%20over%20the%20last%20five%20trading%20days%20with%20234%2C628%20buy%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20customers%20are%20certainly%20a%20faithful%20bunch.%20%231%20NVDA%20brought%20immense%20success%20to%20many%20of%20them%2C%20and%20they%20are%20clearly%20not%20willing%20to%20abandon%20that%20name%20even%20if%20some%20poorly%20received%20earnings%20get%20in%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steve%20Sosnick%2C%20chief%20strategist%20at%20Interactive%20Brokers%2C%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20not%20only%20the%20most%20active%20stock%20on%20our%20platform%2C%20displacing%20%233%20PLTR%2C%20last%20week's%20surprise%20leader%2C%20but%20also%20representing%20just%20under%201%2F3%20of%20all%20the%20net%20purchasing%20activity%20among%20the%20stocks%20in%20this%20table.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-trading-strategy-buy-signal-short-ratio