%20investor%20who%20hosts%20the%20%26quot%3BFriends%20That%20Invest%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20episode%20this%20week%2C%20Kaur%20spoke%20about%20money%20%26quot%3Bmyths%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20the%20notion%20that%20money%20can't%20buy%20happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20more%20money%20doesn't%20necessarily%20improve%20emotional%20well-being%20or%20happiness%2C%20she%20said%2C%20it%20just%20helps%20to%20solve%20inconveniences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20find%20that%20wealthy%20people%20have%20what%20I%20like%20to%20call%20this%20inconvenience%20buffer%2C%20and%20the%20more%20wealth%20you%20have%20up%20to%20that%20certain%20point%2C%20the%20larger%20your%20inconvenience%20buffer%20grows%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20people%20become%20wealthier%2C%20their%20financial%20position%20creates%20more%20of%20a%20cushion%20for%20when%20something%20goes%20wrong%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolumbia-international-student-gave-up-american-dream-immigration-job-market-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20much%20of%20an%20inconvenience%20buffer%20at%20all%20because%20I%20didn't%20have%20extra%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20missed%20a%20flight%20or%20if%20I%20lost%20%2450%20or%20if%20I%20just%20did%20something%2C%20my%20car%2C%20you%20know%2C%20got%20crashed%20or%20I%20had%20a%20dental%20emergency%2C%20those%20things%20really%20affected%20my%20day-to-day%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaur%20said%20that%20these%20setbacks%20were%20so%20stressful%20they%20could%20%26quot%3Bruin%26quot%3B%20her%20week%20or%20month.%20Wealthy%20people%20have%20a%20financial%20buffer%20that%20makes%20this%20easier%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaur%20said%20that%20as%20she%20grew%20richer%20from%20investing%2C%20she%20realized%20that%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20