20settings%20like%20AIIMS%2C%20high%20therapy%20costs%2C%20and%20inadequate%20enforcement%20of%20inclusive%20education%20policies.%20Clearer%20mandates%2C%20standardisation%2C%20and%20periodic%20audits%2C%20she%20says%2C%20are%20essential%20for%20meaningful%20inclusion.%20For%20now%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%E2%80%99s%20a%20sordid%20state%20of%20affairs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaught%20in%20this%20messy%20reality%2C%20many%20parents%20take%20desperate%20steps%20%E2%80%94%20either%20avoiding%20a%20diagnosis%20altogether%2C%20or%20rushing%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfix%2C%20fix%2C%20fix%E2%80%9D%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Anita%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CParents%20lose%20the%20early%20years%20in%20doctor%20shopping.%20It%E2%80%99s%20very%20clear%20that%20they%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20work%20with%20their%20children%20and%20recognise%20their%20individuality%2C%20because%20they%20have%20only%20been%20looking%20for%20solutions%20everywhere.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20experts%20agree%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20tragedies%3A%20%E2%80%9CEverybody%20works%20with%20the%20children%2C%20nobody%20works%20with%20the%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20mothers%20shoulder%20the%20most%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20parenting%20neurodivergent%20children%2C%20the%20main%20onus%20often%20falls%20on%20the%20mother.%20She%20takes%20the%20blame%2C%20carries%20the%20guilt%2C%20and%20remains%20the%20most%20invested%20in%20supporting%20her%20child%20%E2%80%94%20juggling%20therapies%2C%20and%20explaining%20the%20diagnosis%20to%20immediate%20and%20extended%20families%20who%20are%20often%20unsupportive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Swaati%20first%20received%20Aadi%E2%80%99s%20assessment%2C%20she%20felt%20miserable.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20given%20to%20you%20like%20this%20report%20card%2C%20this%20really%20bad%20CV.%E2%80%9D%20From%20there%20begins%20the%20whirlwind%20of%20therapies%2C%20which%2C%20s